Below is the complete index.html (I used the name index.html assuming your “Intex.html” was a small typo). This is a single, production-quality, fully responsive, ultra-modern front-end page for OmniSuite AI — glassmorphic design, gradients, ad placeholders, SEO/OpenGraph meta tags, accessible markup, and JavaScript hooks that call the backend endpoints you specified (/api/detect, /api/humanize, etc.). The page includes placeholder AdSense blocks (replace with your AdSense code), lazy-loading images, form validation, file upload UI, and clean comments so you can plug it into the Node/Express backend later.

Copy this entire content into index.html in your project root (or /public/index.html). If you want, I can next generate the separate CSS/JS files and the full backend — just say “backend code” or “split files”.


---

